                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Düşen Gezegen"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Minyon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Son Aşama:</span> 1 <span style=\"color: #FFE699\">Toprak Hasarı </span>verir.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Kullanım Hakkı: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/29/25073864/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_9071403080740290153.png",
                "id": "talent19581",
                "key": "Dikili Taş",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/29/25073864/905fb3dd007f1806491f7e9df8812d45_5649931337802975587.png",
                "title": "Dikili Taş"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Zaten uygulanmış olan Elementlerle tepkimeye girer:</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Toprak </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Buz</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Buz Kristalleşmesi:</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve aktif karakterin 1 Kalkan puanı kazanır. (üst üste birikebilir ve maksimum 2 puan).</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Toprak </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Su</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Su Kristalleşmesi: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve aktif karakterin 1 Kalkan puanı kazanır. (üst üste birikebilir ve maksimum 2 puan).</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Toprak </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Ateş</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Ateş Kristalleşmesi: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve aktif karakterin 1 Kalkan puanı kazanır. (üst üste birikebilir ve maksimum 2 puan).</span></p><ol><li><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Toprak </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Elektrik</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Elektrik Kristalleşmesi: </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Bu seferki Hasar 1 artar ve aktif karakterin 1 Kalkan puanı kazanır. (üst üste birikebilir ve maksimum 2 puan).</span></p></li></ol>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/29/25073864/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_8851874922262095296.png",
                "id": "talent29357",
                "key": "Toprak Hasarı",
